Text: Re morningDias Corazon Como va todo Me tienen super ocupada en el trabajo estos dias no me quedan suficientes horas en el dia Parece que va a hacer otro dia precioso en Houston aunque un poco caliente Espero que tengas un dia fabuloso Good morning Dear How is everything going They have me super busy at work these days there are not enough hours in the day It looks like its going to be another gorgeous day in Houston althought a lttle hot I hope that you have a great day AM Good Morning How are you doing today me

Re morningtrips arent nice Things have been a little hectic around here and one of my best friends had surgery so I was back and forth to the hospital All is well How are things going for you Are you guys going out tonight Also hope that you have a wonderful weekend but I actually mean it PM Hey Thanks for the emails yesterday Have a nice weekend if I dont talk to you Step

Re Bouquet of Roses from Joefor the roses Joe my first today Joe PM Hello Joe has just sent you a greeting card from Bluemountaincom You can pick up your personal message here cardsboxcvcwitsuznphxhtml Your card will be available for the next days This service is FREE Have a good day and have fun Accessing your card indicates agreement with Blue Mountains Website Rules homeWebsiteRuleshtml Send FREE Blue Mountain cards to friends and family and attach gifts too

Re morningzero money but didnt lose much either Ill pass on the rodeo Im still recovering from a week of birthday celebrations topped by a weekend in Las Vegas thanks for the invitation though I didnt realize that you were moving this weekend For some reason I thought that it was another day I have to help a friend move tonight Unfortunately I dont think that Ill be able to pitch in for your move this weekend because Ill be in NY Sorry although you probably have your hands full with the hourly boys helping you Enjoy the day AM Good Morning So you went to Las VegasThats awesome Did you win lots of money I didnt do muchI played golf yesterday and got some sun on my faceIt was so beautiful yesterday I cant wait for the summer I think Im leaving early and finish some packing Im moving this weekend So If I dont email you again its nothing personal Have a great day and dont work to hard I think were going to the rodeo tonight If you want to go just give me a call Anyway Ill talk to you tomorrow if I dont hear from you tonight me
